WEBVTT

01:34.600 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:39.200 --> 01:40.280
Wen Yifan.

01:42.120 --> 01:43.320
Am I just your backup option?

02:15.840 --> 02:16.960
Goodbye.

02:18.560 --> 02:19.520
Goodbye.

03:00.320 --> 03:02.120
NEWS INTERVIEW VAN
NANWU TV'S FIRST NEWS TEAM

03:02.200 --> 03:03.880
SIX YEARS LATER

03:07.680 --> 03:08.680
They are chasing too closely.

03:09.680 --> 03:11.320
It's fine. Keep steady.

03:13.800 --> 03:14.800
Where do we go?

03:16.640 --> 03:18.040
Turn left!

03:30.800 --> 03:32.000
Be careful!

03:47.240 --> 03:48.760
You're running pretty fast, huh?

03:48.840 --> 03:49.960
- Run again?
- You want to race me?

03:50.040 --> 03:51.280
Get down!

03:51.360 --> 03:52.280
- Hurry up and open the door!
- Open it!

03:53.080 --> 03:53.920
Open it. Don't you hear me?

03:54.000 --> 03:55.040
Get down!

03:55.120 --> 03:56.360
Hurry up!

03:56.440 --> 03:58.160
Lower it. Lower the window!

03:59.040 --> 04:01.240
- I'm lowering it, sir.
- You're racing me, huh? Where's the stuff?

04:01.320 --> 04:02.280
It's on the back seat!

04:09.320 --> 04:10.320
Nanwu TV, huh?

04:11.200 --> 04:12.280
I'll remember you.

04:12.360 --> 04:13.880
Don't make me smash your TV station!

04:24.240 --> 04:25.680
What should we do, Yifan?

04:26.720 --> 04:27.880
Safety comes first.

04:29.720 --> 04:30.760
Wen Yifan.

04:30.840 --> 04:32.560
I don't care how well
you did at Yihe Daily,

04:32.640 --> 04:34.400
that traditional paper media,

04:34.480 --> 04:36.160
but if you can't adjust to the work here,

04:36.240 --> 04:37.920
I'm sorry, you'll be made redundant

04:38.000 --> 04:39.760
once the probation period is over.

04:41.640 --> 04:42.760
What's that sound?

04:44.560 --> 04:45.560
Get out of the car.

04:53.600 --> 04:54.440
- Call an ambulance.
- Yifan,

04:54.520 --> 04:56.120
should I use my phone
to get some material first?

04:56.200 --> 04:57.720
What's more important?
Saving lives or reporting?

04:59.160 --> 05:00.400
Hello.

05:01.000 --> 05:04.440
There's been a car accident.
I'm in the Binjiang District…

05:04.520 --> 05:05.360
Hongguang Avenue…

05:05.440 --> 05:07.040
Yes!

05:07.120 --> 05:08.400
Please come quickly.

05:09.320 --> 05:10.480
Wait a second.

05:10.560 --> 05:11.640
Come on.

05:15.200 --> 05:16.680
Give me your hand!

05:16.760 --> 05:18.080
- Help!
- Be careful.

05:18.160 --> 05:19.440
- Take care.
- Don't let go!

05:19.520 --> 05:20.560
We're done for!

05:23.640 --> 05:24.680
Be careful!

05:26.520 --> 05:27.720
Thank you!

05:58.560 --> 05:59.800
What are you doing?

05:59.880 --> 06:02.120
What's wrong? I'm doing laundry.

06:02.200 --> 06:03.920
I didn't plan on mixing
my clothes with yours,

06:04.000 --> 06:05.160
so I washed them first this time.

06:05.240 --> 06:07.560
And don't think
I'm afraid of you, alright?

06:07.640 --> 06:09.480
Always complaining to the landlord.

06:09.560 --> 06:10.880
I'm not buying into that!

06:24.960 --> 06:25.800
Let go!

06:51.040 --> 06:51.920
Hello, Qiao.

06:52.520 --> 06:54.760
You finally picked up the phone!

06:54.840 --> 06:56.560
Do you know who I just ran into?

06:56.640 --> 06:59.320
I ran into my high school deskmate.

06:59.400 --> 07:01.440
The really handsome vice monitor.

07:01.520 --> 07:03.320
The key point is,

07:03.400 --> 07:05.200
I'm a mess,
with my hair all over the place.

07:05.280 --> 07:07.640
Since this morning,
I've taken ten orders already.

07:07.720 --> 07:08.760
I'm in such a bad state.

07:08.840 --> 07:10.560
It's so embarrassing.

07:10.640 --> 07:11.920
Don't worry too much.

07:12.560 --> 07:14.000
What's up? Why did you call?

07:14.080 --> 07:16.200
How about we go out tonight
and have some fun?

07:16.280 --> 07:19.240
Reporter Wen, you've been working
overtime for a whole week.

07:19.320 --> 07:21.440
If you don't take a break,
I'm afraid you'll collapse.

07:22.040 --> 07:22.880
My friend said

07:22.960 --> 07:24.920
a new restaurant bar
just opened on Gastropub Street.

07:25.000 --> 07:26.800
The boss is super handsome.

07:27.960 --> 07:30.320
Why do I hear water running over there?
Are you doing the dishes?

07:31.160 --> 07:33.560
- Washing up.
- Did you just wake up?

07:34.840 --> 07:37.200
It's already 2 p.m.
What were you doing last night?

07:37.280 --> 07:38.600
I couldn't sleep.

07:38.680 --> 07:40.200
Oh, let me take you to check out some men.

07:40.280 --> 07:41.720
Handsome, fresh,

07:42.600 --> 07:44.840
hot, and steamy men.

07:44.920 --> 07:46.560
I don't have the energy to check out men.

07:47.080 --> 07:48.080
Just one quick glance.

07:48.680 --> 07:51.000
Alright, it's a deal then.
Let's not miss out tonight.

07:51.080 --> 07:52.040
Bye.

08:07.160 --> 08:10.000
Are you sure
there is a restaurant bar here?

08:10.080 --> 08:12.600
I pass by here every day after work,
but I've never seen it.

08:17.320 --> 08:20.320
Lately, everyone likes to hang out here,

08:20.400 --> 08:23.240
relaxing, chilling out, and living slowly.

08:25.400 --> 08:27.560
No wonder this place
is called Gastropub Street.

08:28.960 --> 08:30.160
Look, it's over there.

08:30.240 --> 08:31.240
OVERTIME

08:31.320 --> 08:32.640
It's called "Overtime"?

08:32.720 --> 08:34.280
How boring.

08:35.080 --> 08:37.400
What a nice and thoughtful name!

08:37.480 --> 08:39.440
It's basically a safe haven
for office workers.

08:39.520 --> 08:41.840
Imagine it, when your boss calls
and asks where you are at night,

08:41.919 --> 08:43.840
you can just tell them you're at Overtime.

08:45.800 --> 08:47.440
- Is it newly opened?
- Right.

08:47.520 --> 08:49.120
No wonder I haven't noticed it before.

08:49.200 --> 08:50.400
Let's go.

09:06.480 --> 09:07.680
Take a look!

09:16.760 --> 09:18.240
- Let's go inside.
- Okay.

09:28.880 --> 09:31.960
It really is a paradise
for overtime workers.

09:38.240 --> 09:40.120
Is the boss absent?

09:40.880 --> 09:43.160
Hello, ladies. What can I get for you?

09:43.240 --> 09:45.120
Don't worry.
We'll take care of it ourselves.

09:45.200 --> 09:47.240
Okay. If you need anything,
just scan to order.

09:47.320 --> 09:48.280
Alright.

09:49.480 --> 09:52.440
Could the boss be
that waiter from earlier?

09:52.520 --> 09:53.520
No way.

09:53.600 --> 09:57.600
The boss here is basically
the headliner of Gastropub Street.

10:02.320 --> 10:03.640
The person next to him?

10:04.320 --> 10:05.600
Probably not.

10:18.040 --> 10:19.160
Oh, right.

10:19.240 --> 10:22.480
Didn't I tell you earlier
that I ran into a guy on the road?

10:22.560 --> 10:24.680
He's the vice monitor
from our first year of high school.

10:24.760 --> 10:26.880
I heard he also went to Nanwu University,

10:27.880 --> 10:31.200
and he was in the same class
as your classmate, Sang Yan.

10:31.280 --> 10:33.200
But I haven't really seen him since.

10:33.920 --> 10:35.760
Speaking of which. Do you remember Sang…?

10:41.400 --> 10:43.400
Look! Is that the boss
of the restaurant bar?

10:43.480 --> 10:45.400
- I haven't finished ordering.
- Come over and take a look!

10:46.360 --> 10:48.280
Look. Is it him?

10:50.440 --> 10:51.720
Quick, take a look.

10:51.800 --> 10:53.520
That handsome figure from behind.

10:53.600 --> 10:55.160
How could it be him?

10:59.360 --> 11:00.360
Enough. Stop staring.

11:02.000 --> 11:03.200
Sorry!

11:03.800 --> 11:04.920
How could you be so careless?

11:05.000 --> 11:06.040
It's fine.

11:06.120 --> 11:07.120
I'll go to the restroom.

11:07.200 --> 11:08.760
It can be washed off, right?

11:08.840 --> 11:10.040
I'm so sorry.

11:10.920 --> 11:12.800
- Sorry.
- It's okay.

12:06.160 --> 12:07.720
I saw you earlier.

12:25.720 --> 12:27.160
Change into this.

12:27.240 --> 12:29.360
I'm the boss here. My surname is Sang.

12:29.960 --> 12:31.200
He doesn't recognize me…

12:31.280 --> 12:33.280
I'm sorry. Due to our mistake,

12:33.360 --> 12:34.880
we caused you trouble and inconvenience.

12:34.960 --> 12:36.760
If you ever need anything,
feel free to tell me.

12:36.840 --> 12:40.560
Also, your order is on the house.

12:41.280 --> 12:42.840
I hope it doesn't ruin your good mood.

12:42.920 --> 12:44.600
Looks like he really doesn't recognize me.

12:44.680 --> 12:46.280
Don't worry. It's okay.

12:46.360 --> 12:47.400
I'll be going.

12:48.200 --> 12:49.480
Sang…

12:54.120 --> 12:55.880
Well, I should pretend not to know him.

12:56.720 --> 12:57.560
The Headliner…

12:58.760 --> 12:59.600
Your coat.

13:01.160 --> 13:04.000
Sang… The Headliner?

13:08.000 --> 13:08.960
Sorry,

13:09.480 --> 13:11.160
we are a proper restaurant bar here.

13:12.600 --> 13:13.960
That's quite a shame.

13:15.200 --> 13:17.520
Aren't you happy wearing my clothes?

13:17.600 --> 13:19.480
Seems like I'm more famous than Overtime.

13:20.000 --> 13:21.400
Take it as a souvenir.

13:37.520 --> 13:38.600
You're back.

13:41.200 --> 13:43.400
I just met the boss in the restroom.

13:43.480 --> 13:44.520
He said…

13:46.240 --> 13:47.880
He really said that?

13:49.480 --> 13:51.920
Why didn't he tell you
to frame it at your house?

13:52.680 --> 13:54.080
That's exactly what he meant.

13:55.520 --> 13:57.920
- But don't mind what he said.
- Handsome, we want to order.

13:58.000 --> 13:59.560
After all, he's the star attraction here.

13:59.640 --> 14:00.560
Let me take a good look at him.

14:00.640 --> 14:02.800
- Really?
- Of course.

14:03.400 --> 14:06.240
- Handsome, we want to order here.
- What do you need?

14:06.320 --> 14:09.040
- Alright.
- Why is there someone next to him?

14:09.120 --> 14:10.720
He's got such good luck with ladies.

14:13.560 --> 14:15.160
Hello. Here's your drink.

14:15.240 --> 14:16.840
And here's your refund.

14:16.920 --> 14:18.320
What's this about?

14:18.400 --> 14:20.560
Sorry, it was my mistake earlier.

14:20.640 --> 14:23.000
The boss said
that this table's on the house.

14:23.080 --> 14:25.600
It's not that serious.
Take the money back.

14:25.680 --> 14:27.800
It's okay. It's common for men
to buy drinks for pretty ladies.

14:28.840 --> 14:29.840
Thank you.

14:37.360 --> 14:38.600
Where's the boss?

14:42.560 --> 14:43.600
Give me a drink.

14:59.040 --> 15:00.560
She didn't accept it?

15:00.640 --> 15:03.800
Sir, this might not be
money for the drink.

15:04.480 --> 15:07.120
I just heard those two customers saying…

15:07.200 --> 15:09.240
You've forgotten why you came here?

15:09.840 --> 15:12.840
How could a simple "look"
do justice to his elegance?

15:15.760 --> 15:18.480
This could be something for you…

15:19.240 --> 15:20.240
What thing?

15:20.760 --> 15:22.040
A tip.

15:24.600 --> 15:26.040
Sir, will you accept it?

15:27.720 --> 15:29.000
I'll get back to work.

15:30.360 --> 15:32.200
Sir, what's going on?

15:32.720 --> 15:34.360
Our bar's not that desperate yet, are we?

15:34.440 --> 15:36.000
You're really going the extra mile.

15:58.200 --> 16:00.040
Yifan, how's the house I found for you?

16:00.120 --> 16:01.800
Are you settling in alright?

16:01.880 --> 16:03.720
Although the environment isn't that great,

16:03.800 --> 16:06.000
at least it's convenient
for transportation.

16:06.080 --> 16:07.760
This should make
your commute a bit easier.

16:08.360 --> 16:10.200
If I hadn't chosen to separate from him

16:11.400 --> 16:13.240
back in high school,

16:14.080 --> 16:15.880
what would I be like now?

16:18.080 --> 16:19.600
Would I be happier than now?

16:20.120 --> 16:21.800
And braver?

16:23.560 --> 16:27.320
In this world, is there really another me?

16:30.640 --> 16:32.440
In a parallel universe,

16:33.200 --> 16:35.960
she might walk
a completely different path than mine.

16:37.960 --> 16:39.840
If we met at this moment,

16:41.320 --> 16:44.640
I wonder how the other me would see me.

17:10.839 --> 17:12.079
Yifan,

17:13.000 --> 17:14.960
are you listening?

17:15.800 --> 17:16.920
What did you say?

17:17.000 --> 17:20.079
I said, are you settling in alright
in the house I found for you?

17:21.800 --> 17:23.000
It's fine, I guess.

17:23.720 --> 17:24.839
Then that's good.

17:26.720 --> 17:27.920
This is my station.

17:28.000 --> 17:29.720
Be safe and text me when you get back.

17:29.800 --> 17:31.760
- Alright. Take care.
- Bye.

19:00.200 --> 19:01.840
You're back so late.

19:02.360 --> 19:03.760
I'm not washing my clothes
with yours today.

19:03.840 --> 19:05.000
I've washed them first.

19:05.080 --> 19:06.480
You're back. Eat with us?

19:06.560 --> 19:07.760
No, thanks.

19:07.840 --> 19:10.080
Come on, Yifan. Come eat with us.

19:10.160 --> 19:11.600
No, thanks.

19:16.720 --> 19:19.560
Sir, can you stop
acting like this all the time?

19:19.640 --> 19:20.720
When my wife did
the laundry in the summer,

19:20.800 --> 19:21.800
you threw your clothes in there too.

19:21.880 --> 19:22.840
Isn't that disgusting?

19:22.920 --> 19:24.040
What about the risk of infection?

19:24.120 --> 19:25.920
What infection? I'm pure and clean!

19:26.000 --> 19:27.520
I shower every two days!

19:27.600 --> 19:29.360
You've got a skin condition
and athlete's foot!

19:29.440 --> 19:30.520
I'm very clean!

19:30.600 --> 19:32.520
I'm telling you, I'm warning you,

19:32.600 --> 19:33.840
don't act like this again!

20:07.840 --> 20:09.480
Lady, what would you like to drink?

20:12.680 --> 20:15.280
When we came here for dinner last night,
we dropped a bracelet.

20:15.360 --> 20:16.440
Did anyone find it?

20:16.520 --> 20:18.160
Bracelet?

20:20.720 --> 20:23.320
Last night,
which table were you sitting at?

20:24.160 --> 20:26.280
That one. The first table.

20:26.360 --> 20:27.240
These past two days,

20:27.320 --> 20:30.400
I've been checking lost items.
I really haven't seen a bracelet.

20:30.480 --> 20:31.960
Zhuo, come over here.

20:32.040 --> 20:34.280
This lady was sitting
at that table last night.

20:34.360 --> 20:35.480
Did you find a bracelet?

20:37.520 --> 20:39.720
I accidentally
bumped into you that day. Sorry.

20:40.320 --> 20:41.720
Mr. Yan cleaned the place last night.

20:41.800 --> 20:44.960
When he took the clothes,
he probably took the bracelet, too.

20:48.120 --> 20:50.000
It's okay.
I'll leave my contact information.

20:50.080 --> 20:51.200
Okay.

20:52.480 --> 20:54.200
You can write it down here.

20:54.280 --> 20:55.240
OVERTIME

20:58.880 --> 21:00.760
I'm the bartender here.
My name's He Mingbo.

21:00.840 --> 21:03.520
If there are any further questions,
you can contact me anytime.

21:03.600 --> 21:04.960
Please call me if you find it--

21:11.320 --> 21:12.360
Not giving up.

21:12.880 --> 21:14.600
Even coming specifically
to leave contact info?

21:16.560 --> 21:19.080
Sir, she dropped a bracelet last night.

21:19.160 --> 21:20.360
Well, go find it.

21:20.440 --> 21:21.760
Don't let the customer think
we're slacking off.

21:21.840 --> 21:24.640
Sir, I check the lost items every day.
No bracelet.

21:26.560 --> 21:28.200
Are you sure there is no bracelet?

21:29.000 --> 21:30.840
That's impossible.
What are you talking about?

21:30.920 --> 21:32.240
I check every day.

21:32.840 --> 21:33.880
No way.

21:34.920 --> 21:35.840
It couldn't be there.

21:46.600 --> 21:47.440
Oh…

21:48.080 --> 21:49.280
I found it.

21:49.360 --> 21:50.640
Is this yours?

21:55.240 --> 21:56.680
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

22:03.040 --> 22:04.520
Wasn't there no bracelet when you checked?

22:04.600 --> 22:05.800
Yes.

22:22.160 --> 22:23.560
The bracelet has been found?

22:23.640 --> 22:24.960
Thanks so much!

22:25.040 --> 22:26.760
That bracelet was a gift
from someone I like.

22:26.840 --> 22:28.480
I'll come by another day to pick it up.

22:28.560 --> 22:29.600
I'm going to deliver the food first.

22:29.680 --> 22:30.880
Love you, Yifan.

22:44.360 --> 22:45.240
Do you want something?

22:45.320 --> 22:46.400
I'm going out to get
some late-night snacks.

22:46.480 --> 22:49.680
- No, thanks.
- Alright, we're off.

23:43.920 --> 23:45.960
- You didn't expect it to be me, huh?
- Let go of me!

23:46.480 --> 23:47.320
- Screaming your lungs out
- Let go of me!

23:47.400 --> 23:48.320
won't do any good!

23:48.400 --> 23:50.640
My wife won't be back
for another two hours!

23:50.720 --> 23:51.960
- Let go!
- Just stay calm

23:52.040 --> 23:53.480
and give in to me!

23:56.000 --> 23:56.920
Don't move!

23:57.000 --> 23:58.480
Are you sure I was just peeking?

23:58.560 --> 24:00.560
Are you sure I didn't install a camera?

24:02.280 --> 24:04.200
You're all alone.

24:04.280 --> 24:06.960
No one will care what happens to you!

24:10.960 --> 24:13.800
- What are you doing?
- I just want to protect you!

24:15.120 --> 24:16.720
Look at you, all alone.

24:17.320 --> 24:18.920
No one's here with you for the holidays!

24:20.240 --> 24:21.600
Call the police!

24:28.680 --> 24:30.480
They hit me.
Look at my face, covered in bruises.

24:30.560 --> 24:32.120
- I'm the victim here!
- I was just doing the right thing.

24:32.200 --> 24:33.520
- Doing the right thing.
- They have an affair!

24:33.600 --> 24:34.440
Let me tell you.

24:34.520 --> 24:36.320
We folks from the Northeast
are all good guys!

24:36.400 --> 24:37.240
You!

24:41.320 --> 24:43.120
Miss Wen, don't worry.

24:43.200 --> 24:46.680
Our people carefully checked your place.

24:46.760 --> 24:49.320
We didn't find any cameras at the scene.

24:49.400 --> 24:51.000
You can go home safely now.

24:54.040 --> 24:55.520
If you're still worried,

24:55.600 --> 24:58.400
should we send an officer
to escort you home?

25:01.440 --> 25:03.240
No need. Thank you.

25:18.800 --> 25:20.480
You're all alone.

25:20.560 --> 25:23.400
No one will care what happens to you!

25:37.840 --> 25:39.080
You want to sleep? Come.

25:39.160 --> 25:40.880
You were just saying you wanted to sleep.

25:46.920 --> 25:48.080
Hi.

26:01.240 --> 26:02.720
It's not your fault.

26:04.800 --> 26:06.720
Take care of yourself and the kid.

26:13.840 --> 26:17.320
Mom, whose fault is it?

26:20.720 --> 26:22.240
Was it my fault?

26:33.720 --> 26:35.920
- Yifan?
- Qiao.

26:36.000 --> 26:38.000
Why are you here so late?

26:40.440 --> 26:42.360
I came to give you the bracelet.

26:42.440 --> 26:43.520
Come on in.

26:44.320 --> 26:45.160
Oh, Yifan is here.

26:45.240 --> 26:47.080
- Aunty.
- Come on. Have some fruit.

26:48.880 --> 26:49.920
Yifan is here!

26:50.000 --> 26:51.240
Yifan is here.

26:51.320 --> 26:52.320
- Hello!
- Come in!

26:52.400 --> 26:53.240
Take a seat!

26:53.320 --> 26:54.680
Come in!

26:56.320 --> 26:57.560
Are you really okay?

27:00.160 --> 27:02.040
Can I stay here tonight?

27:03.240 --> 27:04.720
Of course, no problem.

27:33.760 --> 27:35.000
I need to leave now.

27:35.080 --> 27:36.960
Uncle Zheng drove me here.

27:37.040 --> 27:38.720
He's waiting outside.

27:38.800 --> 27:40.040
I can't let him wait too long.

27:40.120 --> 27:41.280
Call me if anything comes up.

27:41.360 --> 27:43.320
I'll call you back later.

27:45.760 --> 27:46.960
Mom,

27:48.600 --> 27:49.680
I'm begging you.

27:51.040 --> 27:52.240
Please, I beg you.

27:54.640 --> 27:56.640
- Help me.
- Do you feel okay to go home?

27:59.280 --> 28:01.000
Please don't leave me again.

28:14.320 --> 28:16.600
Little rascal, hurry up and come out.

28:16.680 --> 28:18.000
I can't hold it anymore.

28:18.080 --> 28:20.040
You've been in there for ages.

28:20.120 --> 28:21.960
Wushuang, Wuye, time to eat!

28:22.040 --> 28:23.320
- Coming.
- Yifan,

28:23.400 --> 28:24.920
come out for breakfast!

28:28.520 --> 28:30.760
- Good morning, sis.
- Good morning, sis.

28:31.840 --> 28:32.840
Good morning.

28:32.920 --> 28:34.320
Yifan, you're awake.

28:34.400 --> 28:35.880
Come out for breakfast!

28:36.480 --> 28:37.680
Let's go. Time to eat.

28:37.760 --> 28:39.640
- Hurry. Sit here.
- Okay.

28:39.720 --> 28:40.560
Eat up.

28:40.640 --> 28:43.080
- Hello, Grandpa.
- Come on. Sit down.

28:43.160 --> 28:44.760
Little rascal, I'm telling you,

28:44.840 --> 28:47.160
you better come out quickly
next time you use the bathroom.

28:47.240 --> 28:48.880
- I know.
- Make sure you remember!

28:48.960 --> 28:50.000
You two, move quickly.

28:50.080 --> 28:52.440
Why are you sitting in my spot again?
Go sit over there. Hurry up!

28:52.520 --> 28:54.840
Come on, Yifan. Help yourself and eat up.

28:54.920 --> 28:56.040
Thank you, Aunty.

28:56.120 --> 28:58.080
Have this lychee-flavored drink.
It'll keep you looking young.

28:59.240 --> 29:00.560
- I want this one.
- You want this one?

29:00.640 --> 29:02.280
Don't be shy. Just eat up.

29:04.640 --> 29:05.880
Move up a little.

29:10.720 --> 29:12.120
This big family is really great.

29:12.200 --> 29:13.160
What's so great about it?

29:13.240 --> 29:15.720
If you keep moving so slowly,
you'll miss the dishes.

29:15.800 --> 29:17.760
Come over often, alright?

29:17.840 --> 29:19.240
I will make you breakfast every day.

29:19.880 --> 29:20.720
Thanks, Aunty.

29:21.320 --> 29:23.360
Look at you. Your studies are great,
and so is your work.

29:25.680 --> 29:27.080
- Hello?
- Yifan,

29:27.160 --> 29:29.840
Mr. Gan and Ms. Qian asked us
to be on time today!

29:29.920 --> 29:31.800
- I'm already here. Hurry up!
- Got it.

29:43.280 --> 29:44.440
She's here!

29:44.520 --> 29:45.640
She's here!

29:46.160 --> 29:47.680
What's going on?
Why are you here so early?

29:47.760 --> 29:49.640
- Fu Zhuang.
- Let's congratulate Yifan.

29:49.720 --> 29:51.520
A round of applause!

29:53.040 --> 29:54.400
Congratulations, Yifan!

29:54.480 --> 29:56.200
- Congratulations, Yifan!
- Hurry!

29:56.280 --> 29:57.840
- Congratulations.
- What's going on?

29:59.400 --> 30:01.640
Yifan, this news is just like your name.

30:01.720 --> 30:03.680
Self-made and extraordinary.

30:04.200 --> 30:05.920
Today, you're the star.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.920
Lin, interview her properly later.

30:08.000 --> 30:09.560
- Okay.
- She's the headline of today's front page.

30:09.640 --> 30:10.960
Alright.

30:11.040 --> 30:12.400
It's about the accident a few days ago.

30:12.480 --> 30:14.000
Miss Wen Yifan,

30:14.080 --> 30:15.800
this certificate of honor

30:15.880 --> 30:17.880
is to commend you for your actions
at the car accident scene.

30:17.960 --> 30:21.040
You remained fearless
and selflessly extended a helping hand.

30:21.120 --> 30:22.040
This is truly deserving of recognition!

30:22.120 --> 30:23.360
Let's give her a round of applause!

30:23.440 --> 30:24.920
FOR DOING A GOOD DEED

30:25.520 --> 30:27.120
We're now at Nanwu TV Station.

30:28.760 --> 30:29.800
Wen Yifan,

30:29.880 --> 30:31.600
can you describe
what the scene was like at that time?

30:31.680 --> 30:32.720
Tell us.

30:32.800 --> 30:35.280
How did you change the minds
of the couple running an illegal business?

30:36.240 --> 30:37.080
Well…

30:37.160 --> 30:39.520
At that moment,
maybe it was another version of me

30:39.600 --> 30:40.560
who acted that bravely.

30:41.160 --> 30:43.040
Most of the time,

30:43.120 --> 30:44.760
I didn't know where she was hiding.

30:44.840 --> 30:46.800
It was just a gut reaction.

30:46.880 --> 30:50.320
They were eventually moved by you
and turned themselves in.

30:50.400 --> 30:51.600
It was instinct?

30:52.280 --> 30:55.360
Yifan, can you tell us in detail

30:55.440 --> 30:58.640
how you gathered such huge courage?

30:58.720 --> 31:00.160
FOR DOING A GOOD DEED

31:00.240 --> 31:01.440
It was…

31:01.960 --> 31:04.120
just a natural reaction.

31:04.200 --> 31:06.160
It's okay. Now, get ready again.

31:06.240 --> 31:07.480
I'll interview you again later.

31:07.560 --> 31:10.360
- Officer, can I interview you?
- Sure.

31:10.440 --> 31:11.760
Let's go over there.

31:15.680 --> 31:17.760
By the way,
help us promote our show, First News.

31:17.840 --> 31:18.920
Ms. Qian.

31:21.600 --> 31:24.160
Come with me
for the New Year's Eve live broadcast.

31:26.160 --> 31:27.440
So, I've been formally hired?

31:28.160 --> 31:29.720
Are you planning to leave?

31:32.160 --> 31:34.400
Everyone, let me make an announcement.

31:34.480 --> 31:37.160
This year's New Year's Eve broadcast
will be planned and executed by Team C.

31:37.240 --> 31:38.720
Other teams, please cooperate.

31:39.320 --> 31:40.400
Did you all hear that?

31:49.040 --> 31:50.480
HAPPY NEW YEAR

31:50.560 --> 31:52.480
HAPPY NEW YEAR

31:57.280 --> 31:59.000
Excuse me. Let us through!

31:59.080 --> 32:01.120
Thank you! Watch out!

32:01.200 --> 32:02.480
Be careful!

32:04.200 --> 32:05.320
I really didn't expect

32:05.400 --> 32:07.680
so many people at the square
for New Year's Eve.

32:07.760 --> 32:08.600
Yeah.

32:08.680 --> 32:10.520
I haven't seen this kind
of atmosphere in a while.

32:10.600 --> 32:12.800
This is the vibe
New Year's Eve should have.

32:22.520 --> 32:25.200
I heard a lot of people
are confessing today.

32:25.280 --> 32:26.360
Really?

32:27.280 --> 32:30.280
You've got quite the big belly.
Who are you expecting to confess to you?

32:30.360 --> 32:32.080
You can't say it like that.

32:32.160 --> 32:34.880
Just because I haven't met someone new
doesn't mean I won't meet an old love.

32:34.960 --> 32:36.800
I had a lot of people
chasing me back then.

32:36.880 --> 32:39.360
- Alright.
- You're about to become a mom.

32:39.440 --> 32:40.920
Why are you still
thinking about old loves?

32:41.440 --> 32:42.680
Just focus on driving.

32:43.360 --> 32:45.840
But have you heard of Murphy's Law?

32:45.920 --> 32:47.760
The more you don't want
something to happen,

32:47.840 --> 32:49.080
the more likely it is to happen.

32:49.160 --> 32:50.520
Today is New Year's Eve.

32:50.600 --> 32:53.360
I believe all miracles will happen!

33:12.840 --> 33:14.360
Yifan, what are you doing?

33:16.120 --> 33:18.040
What's wrong, Yifan? Not feeling well?

33:19.560 --> 33:21.360
Could it be you ran into an old love?

33:22.760 --> 33:24.560
Come on. Stop thinking about old loves.

33:24.640 --> 33:25.600
Don't waste time.

33:25.680 --> 33:26.840
He's here too.

33:31.880 --> 33:33.120
Are we almost there?

33:33.200 --> 33:34.400
- Almost.
- Almost.

33:34.480 --> 33:35.720
The place should be right ahead.

33:37.320 --> 33:38.880
Did he see me just now?

33:42.560 --> 33:43.440
HAPPY NEW YEAR

33:43.520 --> 33:46.920
"Tipsy Night" New Year's Eve Special Sale.

33:47.000 --> 33:50.000
Three-Degree Drinks on sale.
Free for ladies!

33:50.520 --> 33:52.960
Miss, would you like to have a drink?
It's free for ladies.

33:54.040 --> 33:55.520
Handsome, you should have one too.

33:57.280 --> 33:59.600
- How did it end up like this?
- What's wrong with this?

33:59.680 --> 34:01.480
I'm getting double pay tonight!

34:02.240 --> 34:04.040
Would you like to try it too?
It's really good.

34:04.120 --> 34:05.000
No, thanks. I'm working.

34:05.600 --> 34:07.960
- Do you have a mask?
- What's wrong?

34:08.480 --> 34:09.400
I forgot to bring it.

34:09.920 --> 34:11.280
I have one. Here you go.

34:13.679 --> 34:15.400
Aren't you cold, wearing so little?

34:15.480 --> 34:16.760
A little.

34:19.520 --> 34:22.239
- Warm up.
- You're so sweet to me!

34:22.320 --> 34:23.960
A SOLO BAR

34:25.040 --> 34:26.920
I'll take care of things first.
I'll call you later.

34:27.000 --> 34:28.400
- Bye.
- Happy New Year!

34:28.480 --> 34:29.840
Happy New Year!

34:31.120 --> 34:32.520
"Tipsy Night"…

34:32.600 --> 34:34.400
Everyone, hurry and get into position.

34:34.480 --> 34:36.840
The New Year countdown is about to start.
Time waits for no one.

34:36.920 --> 34:38.280
Yifan, let me do it.

34:38.360 --> 34:40.520
Fu Zhuang, hurry up.
Go find the camera position.

34:40.600 --> 34:42.679
Madam, I'll go to the restroom first.

34:42.760 --> 34:43.880
I'll be back soon.

34:43.960 --> 34:45.000
Alright.

34:45.080 --> 34:46.080
Go ahead.

35:04.120 --> 35:05.560
Such a long line.

35:05.640 --> 35:07.840
Why don't you wait here for your sister?

35:07.920 --> 35:09.200
I'll go find your dad first.

35:09.280 --> 35:11.360
She needs me to accompany her here?

35:11.440 --> 35:13.280
With so many people around,
she needs protection.

35:13.880 --> 35:15.160
Besides,

35:15.240 --> 35:17.440
I also want to have
some alone time with your dad.

35:18.080 --> 35:20.680
So, why did you ask me to come out?
To take care of my sister?

35:20.760 --> 35:22.720
You should've figured that out earlier,

35:22.800 --> 35:24.480
then I wouldn't have had
to come up with reasons

35:24.560 --> 35:26.760
to make you come out like now.

35:27.520 --> 35:29.640
Just talk with her for a bit.

35:29.720 --> 35:31.560
She's under a lot of pressure

35:31.640 --> 35:33.040
with the college
entrance exam preparation.

35:33.120 --> 35:34.520
She's lost quite a bit of weight.

35:35.560 --> 35:36.600
Go ahead.

35:40.360 --> 35:42.160
- Little rascal.
- What's up?

35:42.240 --> 35:44.280
I heard you've been
under a lot of pressure lately.

35:44.360 --> 35:45.600
No, I'm not.

35:45.680 --> 35:47.040
Is it just because
of the exam preparation?

35:47.560 --> 35:48.520
I told you, no!

35:48.600 --> 35:49.720
Why worry so much?

35:49.800 --> 35:53.120
I didn't study back then,
but I still got into Nanwu University.

35:53.800 --> 35:55.400
You don't have as much potential as me,

35:55.480 --> 35:58.160
but anyway, you can still study abroad.

36:00.160 --> 36:02.440
Sang Yan actually replied to my message!

36:02.520 --> 36:06.360
The group message I sent him before
has never been replied to.

36:06.440 --> 36:08.080
I thought he wasn't using
this WeChat anymore.

36:09.160 --> 36:10.600
The Nanwu University
you worked so hard to get into,

36:10.680 --> 36:12.440
I could get into without breaking a sweat.

36:12.960 --> 36:13.880
HAPPY NEW YEAR

36:13.960 --> 36:14.800
I didn't get it.

36:15.680 --> 36:16.720
So, it wasn't a group message.

36:16.800 --> 36:18.080
SANG YAN

36:18.160 --> 36:19.560
WECHAT MOMENTS

36:19.640 --> 36:20.520
NOW LOADING

36:21.040 --> 36:22.200
Turns out he blocked me.

36:26.320 --> 36:28.160
You don't want to hear me talk, huh?

36:29.920 --> 36:32.000
Come on. Talk to your real sister.

36:32.080 --> 36:33.680
When did I get a real sister?

36:33.760 --> 36:35.160
Jiaxu, Happy New Year.

36:35.240 --> 36:36.880
Zhi, Happy New Year.

36:37.840 --> 36:39.240
He's your real brother, right?

36:40.480 --> 36:41.320
Help me with the queue.

36:45.280 --> 36:46.320
Sorry.

36:46.920 --> 36:49.440
SANG YAN

36:56.080 --> 36:57.520
HAPPY NEW YEAR!

36:57.600 --> 36:58.600
SEND

36:58.680 --> 36:59.720
SEND TO 36 FRIENDS
SEND

36:59.800 --> 37:00.960
NOW SENDING

37:01.840 --> 37:02.720
HAPPY NEW YEAR!

37:15.880 --> 37:17.760
WHO CAN SEE IT
PRIVATE, ONLY MYSELF

37:17.840 --> 37:20.360
MODIFIED

37:20.440 --> 37:22.200
TODAY

37:35.040 --> 37:36.320
SANG YAN: ?

37:49.680 --> 37:51.880
DO YOU KNOW WHO I AM?

38:19.320 --> 38:21.440
IT'S FINE IF YOU'RE NOT HAPPY

38:41.360 --> 38:42.520
Excuse me.

38:44.600 --> 38:46.920
Hello. Let me through. Thank you.

38:53.040 --> 38:54.280
What's going on?

38:54.920 --> 38:57.200
Yifan, if you had come later,

38:57.280 --> 38:59.480
you'd only see my frozen dead body.

39:01.920 --> 39:04.080
Well, thanks then.
I'm actually short on topics.

39:04.160 --> 39:05.640
It's so cold.

39:07.920 --> 39:09.360
Warm up your hands.

39:10.560 --> 39:11.880
Thanks, Yifan.

39:14.520 --> 39:16.160
Let's interview
some street performers later.

39:16.240 --> 39:17.320
Okay, sure.

39:17.880 --> 39:19.120
Our reporters are currently
at True Love Square,

39:19.200 --> 39:21.560
where the New Year's Eve fireworks
will be held.

39:21.640 --> 39:23.800
It's getting closer to midnight.

39:23.880 --> 39:25.600
The place is already packed with people.

39:25.680 --> 39:27.320
Everyone's looking forward
to the new year's arrival.

39:27.400 --> 39:30.080
Today, we're lucky to interview
the director of Youguang Drama.

39:30.160 --> 39:33.200
Can you explain
the meaning of this creation?

39:33.720 --> 39:36.160
- What's your New Year's wish?
- Not failing my exams!

39:36.680 --> 39:38.440
I hope my deskmate becomes my girlfriend!

39:39.040 --> 39:41.480
You just said it to the camera?
Aren't you afraid your parents will see?

39:41.560 --> 39:43.720
Miss, can I redo this one?

39:43.800 --> 39:45.120
New Year's almost here.

39:45.200 --> 39:46.840
Can you tell us your New Year's wish?

39:47.880 --> 39:50.920
Can you play fewer games
and spend more time with me?

39:51.000 --> 39:52.680
What kind of New Year's wish is that?

39:56.000 --> 39:56.920
Fu Zhuang, did you hear that?

39:58.240 --> 39:59.640
The countdown's about to begin.

39:59.720 --> 40:01.400
Get ready to capture
some close-up shots of the fireworks.

40:01.480 --> 40:02.520
Alright, thanks to both of you.

40:02.600 --> 40:04.840
Happy New Year!

40:05.520 --> 40:06.400
Thanks for your hard work.

40:06.480 --> 40:08.280
You're welcome, Yifan. I'll go ahead.

40:13.440 --> 40:14.440
Ten!

40:14.520 --> 40:16.640
Nine! Eight!

40:16.720 --> 40:17.920
Seven!

40:18.000 --> 40:19.240
Six!

40:19.880 --> 40:21.160
Five!

40:21.240 --> 40:22.400
Four!

40:22.480 --> 40:24.440
Three! Two!

40:25.120 --> 40:26.200
One!

40:26.280 --> 40:29.240
Happy New Year!

40:31.480 --> 40:33.480
Happy New Year!

40:52.720 --> 40:53.920
Sorry.

40:57.800 --> 40:59.240
Happy New Year.

41:05.640 --> 41:07.240
Did he say that to me?

41:32.680 --> 41:39.080
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

42:05.040 --> 42:08.800
- Three! Two! One!
- Three! Two! One!

42:08.880 --> 42:12.400
- Happy New Year!
- Happy New Year!

42:13.560 --> 42:14.800
Happy New Year.

42:16.320 --> 42:18.760
Thanks, bro! You too. Happy New Year!

42:18.840 --> 42:20.520
Thanks for what?

42:21.040 --> 42:22.960
Aren't you wishing me a Happy New Year?

42:23.640 --> 42:25.240
Stop getting too full of yourself.

42:25.320 --> 42:27.160
- I wasn't talking to you.
- Bro…

45:21.440 --> 45:22.280
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:22.360 --> 45:23.200
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
